intro_key1:
name:  Becoming A Programmer
submission_type: url
intro_key3: In this task, you have to learn six new concepts about the dictionary.
intro_key4: First you have to read the three new concepts of the dictionary from `Python`'s website.
intro_key6: Then you have read three new concepts from **stackoverflow**.
intro_key7: You will share your understanding on a Google doc and share it with your mentor and do some questions related to concepts.
intro_key8: You will take a class in which you will explain the new concepts you have learned.
